author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Skywest, Inc. Reports Combined February 2018 Traffic For Skywest Airlines And Expressjet Airlines
text:
March 8 (Reuters) - Skywest Inc:
* SKYWEST, INC. REPORTS COMBINED FEBRUARY 2018 TRAFFIC FOR SKYWEST AIRLINES AND EXPRESSJET AIRLINES
* SKYWEST INC - 135,000 BLOCK HOURS IN FEBRUARY 2018, COMPARED TO 137,100 BLOCK HOURS IN FEBRUARY 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Brief@thomsonreuters.com)
